RT @JackWestMD Agree this is a critical Q & applaud ed board for stating that uncertain or "aspirational" resectability = unresectability. ~20% of pts on perioperative IO trials, which included IIIB NSCLC, were diverted from surgery after being screened as resectable. 

This is a bad outcome.
